1
00:01:31,080 --> 00:01:34,960
[Dream of Golden Years]

2
00:01:35,590 --> 00:01:36,400
Repeat the year?

3
00:01:35,789 --> 00:01:39,539
[2006]

4
00:01:37,039 --> 00:01:37,840
We can't afford

5
00:01:37,840 --> 00:01:39,280
to let her waste another year.

6
00:01:39,280 --> 00:01:40,789
She usually has good grades.

7
00:01:40,789 --> 00:01:42,000
If she hadn't had a fever during the exam,

8
00:01:42,000 --> 00:01:43,590
she would've gotten into a top university.

9
00:01:43,590 --> 00:01:45,479
And she'll do better if she does it again?

10
00:01:45,479 --> 00:01:46,479
And does graduating from a top university

11
00:01:45,670 --> 00:01:48,030
[University Introduction Brochure]

12
00:01:46,479 --> 00:01:47,680
guarantee a good job?

13
00:01:48,120 --> 00:01:49,479
She should apply for a normal school

14
00:01:49,479 --> 00:01:50,580
or a sponsored training program.

15
00:01:50,580 --> 00:01:52,280
She can work right after graduation.

16
00:01:52,280 --> 00:01:53,710
We don't expect her
to support us in our old age,

17
00:01:52,390 --> 00:01:55,020
[Xiangsheng 2006 General Higher Education Admissions
Candidate Preference Form]

18
00:01:54,229 --> 00:01:56,759
but she should at least
stop asking us for money.

19
00:01:56,759 --> 00:01:57,950
Keep your voice down.

20
00:01:57,950 --> 00:01:59,550
Don't let the child hear you.

21
00:02:03,590 --> 00:02:05,980
[Aosheng Normal University]

22
00:02:08,680 --> 00:02:10,419
[Knowledge Can Change Your Life]

23
00:02:15,100 --> 00:02:18,320
[Episode 4: Knowledge Can Change Your Life]

24
00:02:19,270 --> 00:02:19,750
How is it?

25
00:02:19,750 --> 00:02:20,680
Slow down, Meng.

26
00:02:22,150 --> 00:02:23,210
Is it from Xiaolan?

27
00:02:28,030 --> 00:02:28,710
Is it not?

28
00:02:32,520 --> 00:02:33,650
It's from Jiang Yan?

29
00:02:33,910 --> 00:02:35,110
So many letters at it?

30
00:02:35,240 --> 00:02:37,100
You two still write to each other?

31
00:02:37,750 --> 00:02:39,150
I don't know how to reply.

32
00:02:39,630 --> 00:02:41,030
She moved away years ago.

33
00:02:41,280 --> 00:02:42,610
I don't have much to say.

34
00:02:43,430 --> 00:02:45,430
Dating is such a hassle.

35
00:02:45,630 --> 00:02:46,710
She likes you,

36
00:02:46,970 --> 00:02:48,160
yet you like her.

37
00:02:49,630 --> 00:02:50,960
What are you laughing at?

38
00:02:50,960 --> 00:02:52,960
It'll happen to you sooner or later.

39
00:02:58,360 --> 00:02:59,240
Why are you out here

40
00:02:59,240 --> 00:03:00,640
during work hours again?

41
00:03:00,680 --> 00:03:02,430
The job Second Uncle got me

42
00:03:02,430 --> 00:03:03,590
is just for show.

43
00:03:03,630 --> 00:03:05,000
It makes no difference

44
00:03:05,020 --> 00:03:06,360
whether I'm there or not.

45
00:03:06,360 --> 00:03:07,820
Your workplace is better.

46
00:03:08,520 --> 00:03:09,120
By the way,

47
00:03:09,190 --> 00:03:09,800
are you going to

48
00:03:09,800 --> 00:03:11,260
report for duty next week?

49
00:03:12,360 --> 00:03:13,960
I haven't decided if I'm going.

50
00:03:13,960 --> 00:03:15,120
What's there to think about?

51
00:03:15,120 --> 00:03:16,470
Isn't that what life is?

52
00:03:16,470 --> 00:03:17,750
School, work,

53
00:03:18,030 --> 00:03:19,000
marriage, kids.

54
00:03:19,520 --> 00:03:20,590
Now that high school is over,

55
00:03:20,590 --> 00:03:21,590
it's time to work.

56
00:03:22,030 --> 00:03:23,560
It's the same for everyone.

57
00:03:26,870 --> 00:03:28,530
If it's the same for everyone,

58
00:03:29,750 --> 00:03:31,590
does it mean I have to be the same too?

59
00:03:31,590 --> 00:03:32,750
What else can you do?

60
00:03:33,030 --> 00:03:34,560
At most, we can sneak around

61
00:03:34,870 --> 00:03:36,530
doing some business like now.

62
00:03:37,150 --> 00:03:38,680
When are we going next time?

63
00:03:40,120 --> 00:03:41,120
I was thinking of

64
00:03:41,400 --> 00:03:43,030
going to Anqing again next week

65
00:03:43,030 --> 00:03:44,430
to wrap up that business.

66
00:03:45,150 --> 00:03:46,280
Reselling cigarettes

67
00:03:46,280 --> 00:03:47,470
doesn't violate regulations,

68
00:03:47,470 --> 00:03:48,710
but it's exploiting a loophole.

69
00:03:48,710 --> 00:03:49,800
It's not a long-term solution.

70
00:03:49,800 --> 00:03:50,280
Yeah.

71
00:03:50,470 --> 00:03:52,270
It's really profitable though.

72
00:03:52,310 --> 00:03:53,360
Anyway, I'll listen to you,

73
00:03:53,360 --> 00:03:53,840
Cheng.

74
00:03:54,560 --> 00:03:55,490
Let's go. Get in.

75
00:04:11,710 --> 00:04:12,400
Chen Qing?

76
00:04:12,560 --> 00:04:13,490
Why are you here?

77
00:04:13,630 --> 00:04:14,360
Um, these are

78
00:04:14,560 --> 00:04:16,120
some high school textbooks.

79
00:04:16,120 --> 00:04:16,779
Take a look.

80
00:04:17,070 --> 00:04:17,680
Thank you.

81
00:04:19,390 --> 00:04:20,560
I asked about the school

82
00:04:20,560 --> 00:04:21,269
for you.

83
00:04:21,560 --> 00:04:22,630
No.1 High School

84
00:04:22,630 --> 00:04:24,120
is accepting transfer students now.

85
00:04:24,120 --> 00:04:25,920
But since you only have
a middle school diploma,

86
00:04:25,920 --> 00:04:27,800
you have to take an exam first.

87
00:04:28,190 --> 00:04:29,390
If your score meets

88
00:04:29,390 --> 00:04:30,630
last year's associate degree cutoff,

89
00:04:30,630 --> 00:04:32,090
they'll let you transfer.

90
00:04:32,240 --> 00:04:33,300
But the problem is,

91
00:04:33,630 --> 00:04:34,560
English has been added

92
00:04:34,560 --> 00:04:35,510
to the total score this year,

93
00:04:35,510 --> 00:04:36,840
so it might be harder...

94
00:04:36,920 --> 00:04:37,750
Then what was the cutoff

95
00:04:37,750 --> 00:04:39,240
for science associate degrees last year?

96
00:04:39,240 --> 00:04:40,240
Science degrees?

97
00:04:40,720 --> 00:04:42,720
The total score for science was 690.

98
00:04:42,920 --> 00:04:45,000
And the associate degree cutoff was 350.

99
00:04:45,000 --> 00:04:46,430
You want to study science?

100
00:04:46,430 --> 00:04:46,830
Xiaolan,

101
00:04:46,830 --> 00:04:48,360
I suggest you choose liberal arts.

102
00:04:48,360 --> 00:04:49,580
If it's liberal arts, I can...

103
00:04:49,580 --> 00:04:50,000
So,

104
00:04:50,120 --> 00:04:51,580
when is the transfer exam?

105
00:04:52,159 --> 00:04:53,040
Next Monday.

106
00:04:53,800 --> 00:04:55,400
That's less than a week away.

107
00:04:55,650 --> 00:04:56,909
It's going to be tough.

108
00:04:57,600 --> 00:04:58,200
Thank you.

109
00:04:59,040 --> 00:05:00,720
L-L-Let me help you push the bike.

110
00:05:00,720 --> 00:05:01,600
No need.

111
00:05:01,630 --> 00:05:02,230
It's okay.

112
00:05:02,480 --> 00:05:03,210
Here, let me.

113
00:05:03,480 --> 00:05:04,540
You hold the books.

114
00:05:04,560 --> 00:05:05,160
Thank you.

115
00:05:05,830 --> 00:05:07,330
I was a science student originally.

116
00:05:07,330 --> 00:05:10,130
Switching to liberal arts now
would be a disaster.

117
00:05:14,040 --> 00:05:15,310
I'll get going then.

118
00:05:15,830 --> 00:05:16,630
Okay, thanks.

119
00:05:25,240 --> 00:05:25,800
Xiaolan.

120
00:05:26,870 --> 00:05:27,600
Chen Qing brought you

121
00:05:27,600 --> 00:05:28,560
so many books?

122
00:05:29,750 --> 00:05:30,800
Chen Qing prepared

123
00:05:30,800 --> 00:05:32,460
these study materials for me.

124
00:05:32,770 --> 00:05:33,560
I plan to go take

125
00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:35,190
No.1 High School's exam on Monday.

126
00:05:35,190 --> 00:05:35,800
Xiaolan,

127
00:05:36,070 --> 00:05:37,800
you are really going to take it?

128
00:05:39,390 --> 00:05:40,630
I remember before,

129
00:05:40,630 --> 00:05:41,720
when you were in middle school,

130
00:05:41,720 --> 00:05:43,000
your mom asked
if you wanted to go to high school,

131
00:05:43,000 --> 00:05:44,040
and you said no.

132
00:05:44,040 --> 00:05:45,900
Why do you want to study again now?

133
00:05:47,600 --> 00:05:49,060
Doesn't it say on the wall?

134
00:05:49,480 --> 00:05:50,950
"Knowledge can change your life."

135
00:05:50,950 --> 00:05:52,159
I think it's right.

136
00:05:52,680 --> 00:05:53,630
And I think

137
00:05:53,630 --> 00:05:55,430
I need an urban household registration.

138
00:05:55,430 --> 00:05:56,720
Doesn't getting into college

139
00:05:56,720 --> 00:05:59,250
guarantee an urban household registration?

140
00:05:59,720 --> 00:06:00,240
Yes.

141
00:06:00,720 --> 00:06:02,780
Studying is definitely a good thing.

142
00:06:04,360 --> 00:06:05,430
But getting into college

143
00:06:05,430 --> 00:06:06,720
isn't that simple.

144
00:06:07,240 --> 00:06:09,190
We don't need to compete

145
00:06:09,190 --> 00:06:10,630
with Xia Ziyu on studying.

146
00:06:10,630 --> 00:06:12,560
We're better than her in many other ways.

147
00:06:12,560 --> 00:06:13,950
I think it's good

148
00:06:13,950 --> 00:06:15,390
that Xiaolan wants to go to college.

149
00:06:15,390 --> 00:06:16,730
Let the Xia family see

150
00:06:17,120 --> 00:06:18,270
how blind they are.

151
00:06:18,870 --> 00:06:20,510
Well, it's certainly good if she gets in.

152
00:06:20,510 --> 00:06:21,970
She'll definitely get in.

153
00:06:22,720 --> 00:06:24,250
Leave the fried cakes to me.

154
00:06:24,560 --> 00:06:26,090
You just focus on studying.

155
00:06:27,670 --> 00:06:29,400
Comrade Liu Fen,

156
00:06:29,560 --> 00:06:31,310
don't get ahead of yourself.

157
00:06:31,310 --> 00:06:32,640
Nothing is certain yet.

158
00:06:32,920 --> 00:06:34,180
I'm going to study now.

159
00:06:41,750 --> 00:06:42,560
If I'm lucky,

160
00:06:42,630 --> 00:06:44,950
I can take next year's
college entrance exam.

161
00:06:44,950 --> 00:06:46,070
English, which might be difficult

162
00:06:46,070 --> 00:06:47,240
for many test-takers now,

163
00:06:47,240 --> 00:06:48,430
is my strength.

164
00:06:49,750 --> 00:06:50,560
All these years

165
00:06:50,560 --> 00:06:52,040
of working in foreign trade sales

166
00:06:52,040 --> 00:06:53,170
wasn't for nothing.

167
00:06:54,830 --> 00:06:56,480
"Knowledge can change your life."

168
00:06:56,480 --> 00:06:58,810
I'll trust this one more time
in this life.

169
00:07:09,630 --> 00:07:10,480
Smells good, doesn't it?

170
00:07:10,480 --> 00:07:11,560
Don't rush.

171
00:07:11,750 --> 00:07:12,610
It's all yours.

172
00:07:13,480 --> 00:07:14,480
Where's the bike?

173
00:07:15,750 --> 00:07:16,360
Xiaolan.

174
00:07:18,560 --> 00:07:19,120
The bike?

175
00:07:19,560 --> 00:07:21,220
Your uncle lent it to someone.

176
00:07:21,270 --> 00:07:22,000
For now,

177
00:07:22,160 --> 00:07:23,560
just stay home and revise.

178
00:07:23,560 --> 00:07:24,870
Don't do any chores.

179
00:07:24,950 --> 00:07:25,830
Go read your books.

180
00:07:25,830 --> 00:07:27,560
We've got things covered here.

181
00:08:07,630 --> 00:08:08,830
Xiaolan is studying.

182
00:08:08,870 --> 00:08:09,340
Get down!

183
00:08:09,340 --> 00:08:09,870
Get down!

184
00:08:11,830 --> 00:08:13,160
Did you hear what Mom said?

185
00:08:13,160 --> 00:08:13,890
Keep it down.

186
00:08:16,560 --> 00:08:18,070
Mom, what's for dinner?

187
00:08:18,480 --> 00:08:20,140
All you think about is eating.

188
00:08:21,120 --> 00:08:22,830
Here comes the fish.

189
00:08:24,240 --> 00:08:24,830
Come on.

190
00:08:25,190 --> 00:08:25,720
Xiaolan,

191
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:26,860
have some fish.

192
00:08:27,190 --> 00:08:28,310
It helps with studying.

193
00:08:28,310 --> 00:08:29,310
Eat more chicken.

194
00:08:29,480 --> 00:08:31,340
Winner, winner, chicken dinner.

195
00:08:34,669 --> 00:08:35,870
Xiaolan, you eat too.

196
00:08:36,270 --> 00:08:37,200
Good boy.

197
00:08:37,240 --> 00:08:38,100
Thank you, Tao.

198
00:09:04,630 --> 00:09:05,290
Don't grab.

199
00:09:07,150 --> 00:09:08,550
You just want to eat it all yourself?

200
00:09:08,550 --> 00:09:09,600
Leaving so early?

201
00:09:12,480 --> 00:09:13,080
Xiaolan,

202
00:09:13,150 --> 00:09:15,030
you sure know how to dress.

203
00:09:15,750 --> 00:09:16,360
It looks

204
00:09:16,790 --> 00:09:17,720
really good!

205
00:09:17,960 --> 00:09:18,550
She's smart.

206
00:09:18,550 --> 00:09:19,750
Smart at everything.

207
00:09:19,870 --> 00:09:20,870
Smart at dressing,

208
00:09:20,870 --> 00:09:21,910
and smart at studying.

209
00:09:21,910 --> 00:09:23,360
-Xiaolan.
-You should wear it when it's cold.

210
00:09:23,360 --> 00:09:24,200
Don't catch a cold.

211
00:09:24,200 --> 00:09:25,000
Take two eggs.

212
00:09:27,200 --> 00:09:28,150
Got everything?

213
00:09:28,390 --> 00:09:29,390
Don't be nervous.

214
00:09:30,120 --> 00:09:31,030
Wait for my good news.

215
00:09:31,030 --> 00:09:31,490
I'm off.

216
00:09:31,870 --> 00:09:32,720
I'll give you a ride.

217
00:09:32,720 --> 00:09:33,320
No need!

218
00:09:33,550 --> 00:09:34,010
I'm off!

219
00:09:36,720 --> 00:09:37,250
Xiaolan,

220
00:09:37,480 --> 00:09:38,740
don't feel pressured.

221
00:09:38,910 --> 00:09:40,640
It's no shame if you don't pass!

222
00:09:41,200 --> 00:09:42,330
What are you saying?

223
00:09:43,120 --> 00:09:44,380
I think she'll be fine.

224
00:09:45,030 --> 00:09:47,200
It's been so long
since she touched a textbook.

225
00:09:47,200 --> 00:09:48,860
She's only revised for a week.

226
00:09:49,160 --> 00:09:50,560
It's normal if she fails.

227
00:09:53,360 --> 00:09:55,930
[Anqing No. 1 High School]

228
00:09:56,000 --> 00:09:58,000
[Teacher's Office]

229
00:10:08,200 --> 00:10:09,030
Xia Xiaolan,

230
00:10:09,390 --> 00:10:10,990
you can start answering now.

231
00:10:15,840 --> 00:10:17,440
Phonetic differentiation.

232
00:10:17,910 --> 00:10:19,320
Find the vowel sound

233
00:10:19,320 --> 00:10:20,380
that is different.

234
00:10:22,270 --> 00:10:23,870
These questions are so kind.

235
00:10:24,080 --> 00:10:25,880
Are they really not free points?

236
00:10:54,360 --> 00:10:55,320
Ma'am, I'm done.

237
00:10:59,080 --> 00:10:59,560
Here.

238
00:11:02,790 --> 00:11:03,270
Ma'am,

239
00:11:03,270 --> 00:11:04,870
when will the results be out?

240
00:11:05,790 --> 00:11:06,850
In just a day or two.

241
00:11:06,910 --> 00:11:08,000
If you pass, I'll have Chen Qing

242
00:11:08,000 --> 00:11:09,080
pass on the message.

243
00:11:09,080 --> 00:11:10,410
Okay. Thank you, Ma'am.

244
00:11:14,440 --> 00:11:15,770
The exam questions these days

245
00:11:15,770 --> 00:11:16,440
are simpler

246
00:11:16,440 --> 00:11:18,840
than what I took for
the National College Entrance Examination.

247
00:11:18,840 --> 00:11:20,440
English is very basic.

248
00:11:20,630 --> 00:11:21,960
Math isn't hard either.

249
00:11:22,080 --> 00:11:23,630
I wasn't a bad student to begin with.

250
00:11:23,630 --> 00:11:25,320
Plus, with a body of this age,

251
00:11:25,520 --> 00:11:27,320
my memory seems pretty good too.

252
00:11:28,440 --> 00:11:30,080
God sent me back to 1983

253
00:11:30,390 --> 00:11:32,000
maybe to give me a real chance

254
00:11:32,690 --> 00:11:34,150
to become a winner in life.

255
00:11:47,960 --> 00:11:48,600
Xia!

256
00:11:48,870 --> 00:11:49,440
Xia.

257
00:11:49,720 --> 00:11:50,520
What's wrong?

258
00:11:52,240 --> 00:11:53,670
W-Why is she here?

259
00:11:56,320 --> 00:11:58,450
She walked out of No.1 High School too.

260
00:12:00,390 --> 00:12:00,870
Oh no.

261
00:12:01,440 --> 00:12:03,700
Is she really trying to get into college?

262
00:12:06,960 --> 00:12:07,630
What are you doing?

263
00:12:07,630 --> 00:12:09,330
I'm going to send a telegram to Ziyu!

264
00:12:09,330 --> 00:12:11,190
I can't count on you for anything.

265
00:12:25,320 --> 00:12:25,750
Fen.

266
00:12:26,320 --> 00:12:26,750
Fen.

267
00:12:27,240 --> 00:12:28,120
Stop standing there.

268
00:12:28,120 --> 00:12:29,030
You've been standing for 2 hours.

269
00:12:29,030 --> 00:12:30,120
Aren't you tired?

270
00:12:34,000 --> 00:12:34,720
Come on.

271
00:12:35,360 --> 00:12:37,360
Xiaolan will be back after the exam.

272
00:12:37,550 --> 00:12:39,150
It's tiring standing there.

273
00:12:39,360 --> 00:12:40,090
Just sit down

274
00:12:40,220 --> 00:12:41,670
and have some sunflower seeds.

275
00:12:41,670 --> 00:12:42,240
Mom!

276
00:12:43,150 --> 00:12:43,720
I'm back.

277
00:12:45,120 --> 00:12:46,150
Xiaolan is back.

278
00:12:47,200 --> 00:12:47,660
Auntie,

279
00:12:48,000 --> 00:12:48,870
I picked out

280
00:12:48,870 --> 00:12:49,840
some new fabric for you.

281
00:12:49,840 --> 00:12:51,000
Stop wearing gray and blue all the time.

282
00:12:51,000 --> 00:12:52,670
Try these bright stripes.

283
00:12:52,690 --> 00:12:53,720
They'll look great as new clothes.

284
00:12:53,720 --> 00:12:54,360
Okay, thank you.

285
00:12:54,360 --> 00:12:55,360
Drink some water.

286
00:12:55,480 --> 00:12:56,340
Thanks, Uncle.

287
00:13:02,150 --> 00:13:03,280
You must be thirsty.

288
00:13:03,710 --> 00:13:04,240
Thirsty.

289
00:13:05,750 --> 00:13:06,950
I'll go inside first.

290
00:13:08,510 --> 00:13:09,200
Xiaolan.

291
00:13:09,440 --> 00:13:10,840
How did you do on the exam?

292
00:13:12,790 --> 00:13:13,390
This kid!

293
00:13:13,410 --> 00:13:14,760
Why are you everywhere?

294
00:13:15,800 --> 00:13:16,330
Xiaolan.

295
00:13:16,510 --> 00:13:17,600
The exam is over.

296
00:13:17,670 --> 00:13:18,870
Let's not dwell on it.

297
00:13:19,270 --> 00:13:19,720
Right.

298
00:13:20,080 --> 00:13:21,200
We talked it over.

299
00:13:21,390 --> 00:13:22,790
We support you going to college.

300
00:13:22,790 --> 00:13:23,390
If it doesn't work out,

301
00:13:23,390 --> 00:13:24,750
start over
from the first year of high school.

302
00:13:24,750 --> 00:13:25,630
Study for 3 years,

303
00:13:25,630 --> 00:13:26,870
and you'll definitely pass
the college entrance exam next time.

304
00:13:26,870 --> 00:13:27,630
Right, right.

305
00:13:27,630 --> 00:13:29,080
It doesn't matter
if it's a bachelor's degree or not.

306
00:13:29,080 --> 00:13:30,480
For our family, even an associate degree

307
00:13:30,480 --> 00:13:31,670
would be a huge blessing.

308
00:13:31,670 --> 00:13:32,030
Right?

309
00:13:32,030 --> 00:13:32,670
Exactly.

310
00:13:32,840 --> 00:13:33,630
As for the money,

311
00:13:33,630 --> 00:13:34,750
you don't need to worry.

312
00:13:34,750 --> 00:13:36,240
I'll go out to work right away

313
00:13:36,240 --> 00:13:37,390
to pay for your college.

314
00:13:37,390 --> 00:13:37,750
I-I

315
00:13:37,750 --> 00:13:40,210
can also earn money
to support your studies.

316
00:13:41,910 --> 00:13:43,840
Thank you, Uncle, Auntie, and Mom.

317
00:13:44,080 --> 00:13:44,670
But I think

318
00:13:44,670 --> 00:13:45,750
I did pretty well.

319
00:13:46,320 --> 00:13:47,710
Maybe you should prepare

320
00:13:47,710 --> 00:13:49,840
for me to take the college entrance exam
next year.

321
00:13:49,840 --> 00:13:51,470
When will the results be out?

322
00:13:51,600 --> 00:13:52,870
In a day or two.

323
00:13:53,080 --> 00:13:54,000
Did you hear that?

324
00:13:54,000 --> 00:13:55,130
She did pretty well.

325
00:13:56,320 --> 00:13:56,830
Dad.

326
00:13:57,120 --> 00:13:58,870
What score is "pretty well"?

327
00:13:59,240 --> 00:14:00,750
We'll know in a couple of days.

328
00:14:00,750 --> 00:14:01,590
Go get dinner ready.

329
00:14:01,590 --> 00:14:02,160
Right.

330
00:14:16,120 --> 00:14:16,720
Ms. Qi,

331
00:14:17,600 --> 00:14:19,130
a parent is looking for you.

332
00:14:19,270 --> 00:14:20,200
Okay, I'll be right there.

333
00:14:20,200 --> 00:14:20,600
Okay.

334
00:14:28,000 --> 00:14:28,720
Here, try it.

335
00:14:28,720 --> 00:14:29,450
Is it too hot?

336
00:14:29,790 --> 00:14:30,390
All right.

337
00:14:33,870 --> 00:14:35,000
Liang has been

338
00:14:35,030 --> 00:14:36,000
rushing me

339
00:14:36,150 --> 00:14:37,240
to go work with him.

340
00:14:38,150 --> 00:14:39,270
The family needs money

341
00:14:39,270 --> 00:14:40,200
right now, too.

342
00:14:41,150 --> 00:14:42,790
So I quickly renewed
the contract with him.

343
00:14:42,790 --> 00:14:43,670
You have to take care

344
00:14:43,670 --> 00:14:45,000
of yourself out there.

345
00:14:45,510 --> 00:14:47,120
Don't worry. I've got things covered here.

346
00:14:47,120 --> 00:14:48,580
I'll take good care of Tao.

347
00:14:48,750 --> 00:14:49,600
As for Fen and Xiaolan,

348
00:14:49,600 --> 00:14:50,390
I won't let them

349
00:14:50,390 --> 00:14:51,600
be mistreated either.

350
00:14:51,600 --> 00:14:52,480
It's going to be

351
00:14:53,150 --> 00:14:54,280
hard on you, though.

352
00:14:54,840 --> 00:14:56,080
It won't wear me out.

353
00:14:56,790 --> 00:14:58,650
Look how sensible Xiaolan is now.

354
00:14:58,870 --> 00:14:59,390
She also

355
00:14:59,430 --> 00:15:00,860
has what she wants to do

356
00:15:01,320 --> 00:15:02,980
in the future all figured out.

357
00:15:03,870 --> 00:15:04,600
That's true.

358
00:15:05,200 --> 00:15:06,360
After going through that ordeal,

359
00:15:06,360 --> 00:15:08,560
it's like she's suddenly enlightened.

360
00:15:08,600 --> 00:15:09,800
Anyway, whether it's

361
00:15:10,030 --> 00:15:10,960
studying

362
00:15:11,120 --> 00:15:12,180
or doing business,

363
00:15:12,360 --> 00:15:13,820
they are all honest paths.

364
00:15:13,870 --> 00:15:15,030
As her elders,

365
00:15:15,270 --> 00:15:16,030
we have to support her.

366
00:15:16,030 --> 00:15:16,630
Of course.

367
00:15:16,630 --> 00:15:17,760
We must support her.

368
00:15:18,200 --> 00:15:18,840
How is it?

369
00:15:19,080 --> 00:15:19,960
Does it feel good?

370
00:15:19,960 --> 00:15:20,750
It does.

371
00:15:22,870 --> 00:15:23,600
Give me a kiss.

372
00:15:23,600 --> 00:15:24,870
Hey!

373
00:15:24,890 --> 00:15:26,250
Just give me a kiss.

374
00:15:29,550 --> 00:15:30,120
Fengmei!

375
00:15:30,360 --> 00:15:31,290
I'm heading out!

376
00:15:33,510 --> 00:15:34,080
Uncle!

377
00:15:35,080 --> 00:15:36,080
Are you going out?

378
00:15:36,360 --> 00:15:37,560
I'm going out to work.

379
00:15:37,630 --> 00:15:39,030
I need to buy some things.

380
00:15:39,750 --> 00:15:40,750
I'll go with you.

381
00:15:42,600 --> 00:15:43,400
Let's go then.

382
00:15:48,000 --> 00:15:49,080
You insist on coming with me

383
00:15:49,080 --> 00:15:50,670
because you have something to say to me?

384
00:15:50,670 --> 00:15:51,910
I have a question for you.

385
00:15:51,910 --> 00:15:52,480
Ask away.

386
00:15:52,750 --> 00:15:54,030
No need to be so mysterious.

387
00:15:54,030 --> 00:15:55,360
I'll ask directly then.

388
00:15:56,840 --> 00:15:57,360
Uncle,

389
00:15:57,960 --> 00:15:59,560
are you really a bricklayer?

390
00:15:59,600 --> 00:16:01,330
You aren't smuggling, are you?

391
00:16:03,270 --> 00:16:05,270
What nonsense are you talking about?

392
00:16:05,270 --> 00:16:07,000
You shouldn't joke about that.

393
00:16:08,240 --> 00:16:09,550
The other day, Chen Qing said

394
00:16:09,550 --> 00:16:10,600
there was a call for you.

395
00:16:10,600 --> 00:16:12,120
You looked nervous.

396
00:16:12,390 --> 00:16:13,790
I felt something was wrong.

397
00:16:13,790 --> 00:16:15,200
And before, you warned me

398
00:16:15,200 --> 00:16:17,200
that Zhou Cheng might be a smuggler.

399
00:16:17,320 --> 00:16:18,180
I was thinking,

400
00:16:18,440 --> 00:16:20,170
if you hadn't done it yourself,

401
00:16:20,440 --> 00:16:21,900
how would you know so much?

402
00:16:22,600 --> 00:16:24,090
I asked Auntie.

403
00:16:24,320 --> 00:16:25,600
Your income as a bricklayer

404
00:16:25,600 --> 00:16:26,750
is too impressive.

405
00:16:27,080 --> 00:16:28,360
Take this bicycle.

406
00:16:28,750 --> 00:16:30,150
It must cost at least 200.

407
00:16:30,240 --> 00:16:31,390
What kind of bricklayer

408
00:16:31,390 --> 00:16:33,080
can afford a bike in 6 months?

409
00:16:33,440 --> 00:16:34,580
I was just guessing,

410
00:16:35,000 --> 00:16:36,460
but seeing your reaction,

411
00:16:37,550 --> 00:16:38,720
I'm probably right.

412
00:16:40,600 --> 00:16:41,270
Xiaolan.

413
00:16:41,600 --> 00:16:43,120
I really am a bricklayer.

414
00:16:43,960 --> 00:16:45,120
It's just that sometimes,

415
00:16:45,120 --> 00:16:45,630
they ask me

416
00:16:45,630 --> 00:16:47,030
to watch over some goods.

417
00:16:47,270 --> 00:16:48,070
But I promise,

418
00:16:48,200 --> 00:16:49,120
I never asked

419
00:16:49,120 --> 00:16:50,250
what the goods were.

420
00:16:51,240 --> 00:16:51,840
Of course.

421
00:16:53,440 --> 00:16:54,270
I believe you.

422
00:16:54,910 --> 00:16:55,670
But business with unknown sources

423
00:16:55,670 --> 00:16:56,930
that makes quick money

424
00:16:57,270 --> 00:16:58,360
is usually dangerous.

425
00:16:58,360 --> 00:16:58,790
Yes.

426
00:16:59,200 --> 00:17:00,720
Making money is important,

427
00:17:00,720 --> 00:17:01,790
but you have to think about your family.

428
00:17:01,790 --> 00:17:02,270
Right?

429
00:17:02,550 --> 00:17:02,960
Yes.

430
00:17:03,390 --> 00:17:04,550
S-So I...

431
00:17:04,680 --> 00:17:05,960
turned down the job

432
00:17:05,960 --> 00:17:07,160
on the phone that day.

433
00:17:07,200 --> 00:17:08,349
Th-This time I really am

434
00:17:08,349 --> 00:17:10,010
going to work as a bricklayer.

435
00:17:11,829 --> 00:17:12,560
Then, Uncle,

436
00:17:13,270 --> 00:17:14,240
what if I said

437
00:17:14,400 --> 00:17:16,069
I have a business that makes money faster,

438
00:17:16,069 --> 00:17:17,550
and I want to partner with you?

439
00:17:17,550 --> 00:17:18,410
Do you trust me?

440
00:17:20,349 --> 00:17:21,349
What business?

441
00:17:22,680 --> 00:17:24,010
I want to go to Longcheng

442
00:17:24,109 --> 00:17:25,040
to sell clothes.

443
00:17:25,960 --> 00:17:27,720
But you're still in school.

444
00:17:27,750 --> 00:17:29,080
How can you do business?

445
00:17:29,750 --> 00:17:30,310
It's precisely because

446
00:17:30,310 --> 00:17:31,840
I want to focus on my studies

447
00:17:31,960 --> 00:17:33,240
that I need an easier,

448
00:17:33,240 --> 00:17:34,640
more profitable business.

449
00:17:34,640 --> 00:17:36,240
When I need to study for exams,

450
00:17:36,240 --> 00:17:38,040
I'll hand the business to my mom.

451
00:17:39,510 --> 00:17:40,270
I know.

452
00:17:40,680 --> 00:17:42,750
You wouldn't let me
go without money for school.

453
00:17:42,750 --> 00:17:44,160
But I'm an adult now.

454
00:17:44,400 --> 00:17:46,000
I should take care of myself.

455
00:17:46,350 --> 00:17:46,830
Uncle,

456
00:17:47,110 --> 00:17:48,640
you understand, don't you?

457
00:17:53,510 --> 00:17:55,110
Actually, over these years,

458
00:17:55,440 --> 00:17:56,550
I've been out and about,

459
00:17:56,550 --> 00:17:58,070
and seen a bit of the world.

460
00:17:58,640 --> 00:18:00,270
The clothing business is doable.

461
00:18:00,270 --> 00:18:01,720
I just don't have the eye for it,

462
00:18:01,720 --> 00:18:03,250
so I never thought about it.

463
00:18:03,480 --> 00:18:05,340
But Xiaolan, I think you can do it.

464
00:18:05,680 --> 00:18:06,680
These days, I feel

465
00:18:06,680 --> 00:18:07,960
that your vision

466
00:18:08,110 --> 00:18:09,680
seems to be ahead of mine.

467
00:18:10,720 --> 00:18:13,050
So if you want to do
the clothing business,

468
00:18:13,160 --> 00:18:14,090
I believe in you.

469
00:18:14,720 --> 00:18:15,590
Thank you, Uncle!

470
00:18:15,590 --> 00:18:17,390
I'll go buy the train ticket now.

471
00:18:18,750 --> 00:18:19,680
Without a letter of introduction,

472
00:18:19,680 --> 00:18:21,480
how are you going to buy a ticket?

473
00:18:22,830 --> 00:18:24,290
A letter of introduction?

474
00:18:29,930 --> 00:18:30,560
Xiaolan.

475
00:18:35,000 --> 00:18:35,440
Look.

476
00:18:36,790 --> 00:18:38,850
I got you the letter of introduction.

477
00:18:39,440 --> 00:18:40,880
I had to ask several people
in Dahe Village

478
00:18:40,880 --> 00:18:42,270
to get it done.

479
00:18:42,790 --> 00:18:44,110
So I was thinking,

480
00:18:44,310 --> 00:18:45,200
we need to transfer

481
00:18:45,200 --> 00:18:47,680
you and your mother's family register
back here as soon as possible.

482
00:18:47,680 --> 00:18:48,680
Thank you, Uncle.

483
00:18:50,270 --> 00:18:51,880
I have to go out to work.

484
00:18:52,720 --> 00:18:53,550
As for Longcheng,

485
00:18:53,550 --> 00:18:55,210
you'll have to go by yourself.

486
00:18:55,440 --> 00:18:56,310
Be careful.

487
00:18:56,750 --> 00:18:57,960
Don't worry, Uncle.

488
00:18:58,200 --> 00:18:59,030
I've been doing business

489
00:18:59,030 --> 00:19:00,030
on my own for so long.

490
00:19:00,030 --> 00:19:01,230
Don't worry about it.

491
00:19:02,070 --> 00:19:02,550
Okay.

492
00:19:05,590 --> 00:19:06,830
These life details

493
00:19:06,830 --> 00:19:07,750
of the 80s,

494
00:19:08,480 --> 00:19:10,080
if Uncle hadn't reminded me,

495
00:19:10,160 --> 00:19:11,820
I really wouldn't have known.

496
00:19:12,580 --> 00:19:13,190
Cheng,

497
00:19:13,270 --> 00:19:14,570
we'll arrive tomorrow.

498
00:19:14,570 --> 00:19:15,700
Why send a telegram?

499
00:19:17,200 --> 00:19:18,030
I have a hunch.

500
00:19:19,030 --> 00:19:19,550
Although we haven't

501
00:19:19,550 --> 00:19:20,610
been away for long,

502
00:19:21,050 --> 00:19:22,400
Comrade Xiaolan's progress

503
00:19:22,400 --> 00:19:24,660
might be changing with each passing day.

504
00:19:24,790 --> 00:19:25,350
If I don't

505
00:19:25,350 --> 00:19:26,880
tell her in advance this time,

506
00:19:26,880 --> 00:19:28,140
we might not even meet.

507
00:19:28,240 --> 00:19:28,510
Let's go.

508
00:19:28,510 --> 00:19:28,960
Okay.

509
00:19:29,640 --> 00:19:30,300
I'll drive.

510
00:19:30,750 --> 00:19:31,350
You drive.

511
00:19:35,680 --> 00:19:36,310
Fengmei.

512
00:19:36,830 --> 00:19:37,760
My brother left?

513
00:19:38,240 --> 00:19:39,770
He left early in the morning

514
00:19:39,830 --> 00:19:40,720
in a rush.

515
00:19:42,070 --> 00:19:43,530
I picked some vegetables.

516
00:19:43,550 --> 00:19:45,070
He should have eaten before leaving.

517
00:19:45,070 --> 00:19:45,870
It's his loss.

518
00:19:45,960 --> 00:19:47,420
We'll eat them ourselves.

519
00:19:47,440 --> 00:19:48,030
Mom!

520
00:19:48,720 --> 00:19:49,680
Mom, Auntie!

521
00:19:50,400 --> 00:19:50,960
Xiaolan.

522
00:19:51,750 --> 00:19:53,880
I've already bought the train ticket.

523
00:19:56,110 --> 00:19:56,840
Xia Xiaolan!

524
00:19:57,270 --> 00:19:57,870
Telegram!

525
00:19:59,110 --> 00:19:59,830
Chen Hongwei!

526
00:19:59,830 --> 00:20:00,400
That's me.

527
00:20:00,400 --> 00:20:00,790
Here.

528
00:20:01,240 --> 00:20:02,110
Wang Zhenzhen.

529
00:20:02,310 --> 00:20:03,000
Mine, mine.

530
00:20:03,550 --> 00:20:04,480
I'm Xia Xiaolan.

531
00:20:04,590 --> 00:20:05,720
Xia Xiaolan, right?

532
00:20:06,110 --> 00:20:07,480
Yours is a telegram.

533
00:20:07,640 --> 00:20:08,590
-A telegram?
-Five of them.

534
00:20:08,590 --> 00:20:09,250
Take a look.

535
00:20:10,200 --> 00:20:11,640
Sign here if everything is fine.

536
00:20:11,640 --> 00:20:13,790
Dayong's family
must have rich relatives in the city.

537
00:20:13,790 --> 00:20:14,720
That's such a thick telegram.

538
00:20:14,720 --> 00:20:16,200
Those are charged by the character.

539
00:20:16,200 --> 00:20:17,530
How much must that cost?

540
00:20:17,750 --> 00:20:18,320
Actually,

541
00:20:18,320 --> 00:20:19,240
if it's nothing urgent,

542
00:20:19,240 --> 00:20:20,440
writing a letter would be enough.

543
00:20:20,440 --> 00:20:20,960
We can

544
00:20:21,120 --> 00:20:22,440
deliver letters here too.

545
00:20:22,440 --> 00:20:23,160
Okay, thank you.

546
00:20:23,160 --> 00:20:23,550
Okay.

547
00:20:23,750 --> 00:20:24,240
Say,

548
00:20:24,240 --> 00:20:25,770
is there a boy who likes her?

549
00:20:26,240 --> 00:20:26,720
No.

550
00:20:27,070 --> 00:20:27,600
Let's go.

551
00:20:28,000 --> 00:20:28,480
Fen.

552
00:20:29,220 --> 00:20:31,150
You're her mother. You have to ask.

553
00:20:32,830 --> 00:20:33,790
Hello, Xiaolan,

554
00:20:34,160 --> 00:20:35,620
Since we parted last time,

555
00:20:35,640 --> 00:20:36,350
although I have long wanted

556
00:20:36,350 --> 00:20:38,200
to come to Anqing to visit you again,

557
00:20:38,200 --> 00:20:40,440
I was tied down
by trivial matters in the capital.

558
00:20:40,440 --> 00:20:41,590
I missed you so much.

559
00:20:42,480 --> 00:20:44,000
I wonder if you

560
00:20:44,000 --> 00:20:45,110
feel the same way.

561
00:20:47,270 --> 00:20:48,750
When you see this letter,

562
00:20:49,790 --> 00:20:51,070
I will have already left the capital

563
00:20:51,070 --> 00:20:51,790
for Anqing.

564
00:20:52,590 --> 00:20:54,050
I should arrive tomorrow.

565
00:20:54,590 --> 00:20:56,750
I will still be staying at the guesthouse.

566
00:20:56,750 --> 00:20:58,750
I hope to see you.

567
00:21:02,000 --> 00:21:02,440
Here.

568
00:21:03,680 --> 00:21:04,210
Xiaolan.

569
00:21:05,720 --> 00:21:06,650
How does it look?

570
00:21:07,590 --> 00:21:08,030
Mom,

571
00:21:08,400 --> 00:21:09,200
what is this?

572
00:21:10,440 --> 00:21:11,720
To hold money.

573
00:21:12,480 --> 00:21:13,920
This is so safe.

574
00:21:14,960 --> 00:21:15,510
Mom!

575
00:21:17,400 --> 00:21:18,440
Ten yuan a note—

576
00:21:18,680 --> 00:21:19,790
six hundred yuan is a thick stack.

577
00:21:19,790 --> 00:21:21,250
Do you think it fits there?

578
00:21:22,750 --> 00:21:23,590
Let me try.

579
00:21:27,510 --> 00:21:28,640
It is a bit too small.

580
00:21:29,160 --> 00:21:29,760
Hold this.

581
00:21:30,590 --> 00:21:31,440
I'll sew a bigger one

582
00:21:31,440 --> 00:21:32,370
right next to it.

583
00:21:32,470 --> 00:21:32,920
Mom!

584
00:21:34,680 --> 00:21:36,280
Why don't you separate them?

585
00:21:36,920 --> 00:21:37,750
Sew another one?

586
00:21:37,750 --> 00:21:38,750
No, no, no.

587
00:21:39,070 --> 00:21:41,400
Sew two more pockets

588
00:21:41,550 --> 00:21:42,610
inside the jacket.

589
00:21:43,160 --> 00:21:44,360
We won't be so unlucky

590
00:21:44,550 --> 00:21:46,750
that a thief steals everything at once.

591
00:21:47,160 --> 00:21:48,110
That's true.

592
00:21:49,030 --> 00:21:50,240
You are so smart, Xiaolan.

593
00:21:50,240 --> 00:21:50,750
Okay.

594
00:21:50,960 --> 00:21:51,560
All right.

595
00:21:53,510 --> 00:21:54,350
The jacket.

596
00:21:54,510 --> 00:21:55,350
Okay, okay.

597
00:21:56,400 --> 00:21:58,110
It's been 4 or 5 days.

598
00:21:58,920 --> 00:22:01,250
Why haven't the exam results come out yet?

599
00:22:02,750 --> 00:22:04,720
I wonder when Zhou Cheng will arrive.

600
00:22:04,720 --> 00:22:05,880
If he misses me,

601
00:22:06,400 --> 00:22:08,130
then we are just not meant to be.

602
00:22:14,960 --> 00:22:15,960
Comrade Xiaolan!

603
00:22:17,830 --> 00:22:19,230
Did you get the telegram?

604
00:22:21,200 --> 00:22:21,750
I did.

605
00:22:27,080 --> 00:22:32,300
[Capital, Haidian District, Capital Normal University, Xia Ziyu]
[Mother and daughter moved away; detained after refusing to move out; Lan took an exam]

606
00:22:29,110 --> 00:22:29,970
Taking an exam?

607
00:22:30,720 --> 00:22:32,050
College entrance exam?

608
00:22:33,110 --> 00:22:34,030
Don't tell me she hasn't

609
00:22:34,030 --> 00:22:34,920
given up on Wang Jianhua yet?

610
00:22:34,920 --> 00:22:35,450
Jianhua.

611
00:22:35,550 --> 00:22:36,750
You have to come
to the match this afternoon.

612
00:22:36,750 --> 00:22:38,680
Exactly. We can't win without you.

613
00:22:39,030 --> 00:22:39,920
Isn't that Xia Ziyu?

614
00:22:39,920 --> 00:22:40,980
Let's go eat first.

615
00:22:41,400 --> 00:22:42,310
Let's not disturb them.

616
00:22:42,310 --> 00:22:42,960
Let's go.

617
00:22:47,070 --> 00:22:48,200
My class ended late.

618
00:22:48,310 --> 00:22:49,680
You could have started eating.

619
00:22:49,680 --> 00:22:50,720
You didn't have to wait for me.

620
00:22:50,720 --> 00:22:51,780
I didn't wait long.

621
00:22:52,000 --> 00:22:54,160
Besides, we are boyfriend and girlfriend.

622
00:22:54,160 --> 00:22:55,400
If I don't care about you,

623
00:22:55,400 --> 00:22:56,930
who else would I care about?

624
00:22:58,550 --> 00:22:59,150
Let's eat.

625
00:22:59,440 --> 00:23:00,110
Okay.

626
00:23:03,720 --> 00:23:04,110
Here.

627
00:23:04,550 --> 00:23:05,110
Thanks.

628
00:23:13,440 --> 00:23:15,350
You gave me all the braised pork again.

629
00:23:15,350 --> 00:23:16,720
You should have some too.

630
00:23:16,720 --> 00:23:18,590
You're a man. You burn more energy.

631
00:23:18,590 --> 00:23:19,390
Eat more meat.

632
00:23:19,550 --> 00:23:20,030
No, you eat some too.

633
00:23:20,030 --> 00:23:20,550
I'm fine with just vegetables.

634
00:23:20,550 --> 00:23:21,110
Have some.

635
00:23:21,110 --> 00:23:22,240
No need. Really.

636
00:23:22,240 --> 00:23:24,240
If you don't eat, I won't eat either.

637
00:23:24,680 --> 00:23:25,480
Be good. Here.

638
00:23:26,270 --> 00:23:28,200
Eat more.

639
00:23:30,070 --> 00:23:30,590
Eat.

640
00:23:33,480 --> 00:23:34,410
Thank you, Ziyu.

641
00:23:35,440 --> 00:23:36,480
It's nothing.

642
00:23:38,070 --> 00:23:39,640
The money you gave me before

643
00:23:39,880 --> 00:23:41,080
really helped me out.

644
00:23:41,400 --> 00:23:42,400
My dad will soon be

645
00:23:42,400 --> 00:23:44,000
reinstated in the education department.

646
00:23:44,000 --> 00:23:44,640
Really?

647
00:23:44,960 --> 00:23:45,760
That's great!

648
00:23:46,110 --> 00:23:48,030
So I really want to thank you,

649
00:23:48,030 --> 00:23:48,510
Ziyu.

650
00:23:50,960 --> 00:23:52,420
You don't need to thank me.

651
00:23:52,440 --> 00:23:54,070
Your family is my family.

652
00:23:57,200 --> 00:23:57,800
Let's eat.

653
00:24:11,160 --> 00:24:12,590
The self-defense item
I gave you last time,

654
00:24:12,590 --> 00:24:13,520
did you bring it?

655
00:24:14,240 --> 00:24:15,170
It's right here.

656
00:24:16,450 --> 00:24:18,050
I just wanted to come see you.

657
00:24:18,200 --> 00:24:18,640
But I didn't expect

658
00:24:18,640 --> 00:24:19,920
your business to grow so big

659
00:24:19,920 --> 00:24:21,480
that you're going to Longcheng for stock.

660
00:24:21,480 --> 00:24:22,610
Why the sudden rush?

661
00:24:23,480 --> 00:24:24,200
Because I plan to

662
00:24:24,200 --> 00:24:25,550
take the college entrance exam next year.

663
00:24:25,550 --> 00:24:27,030
So I want to pave the way first.

664
00:24:27,030 --> 00:24:27,880
Then I can hand the business to my mom

665
00:24:27,880 --> 00:24:29,210
and focus on my studies.

666
00:24:30,110 --> 00:24:31,440
College entrance exam?

667
00:24:32,350 --> 00:24:33,440
Why did you suddenly think of

668
00:24:33,440 --> 00:24:34,270
going to college?

669
00:24:34,270 --> 00:24:35,590
In this era,

670
00:24:35,590 --> 00:24:36,310
isn't going to college

671
00:24:36,310 --> 00:24:37,640
the natural thing to do?

672
00:24:38,270 --> 00:24:40,200
Stop being lazy to stop being poor,

673
00:24:40,400 --> 00:24:41,270
rely on yourself,

674
00:24:41,270 --> 00:24:42,240
work hard,

675
00:24:42,440 --> 00:24:43,680
and knowledge can change your life.

676
00:24:43,680 --> 00:24:44,440
Isn't that what's written

677
00:24:44,440 --> 00:24:45,270
on the slogans?

678
00:24:45,270 --> 00:24:46,730
Shouldn't I believe them?

679
00:24:48,960 --> 00:24:49,620
You should.

680
00:24:50,160 --> 00:24:51,360
Of course you should.

681
00:24:51,960 --> 00:24:52,960
Comrade Xiaolan.

682
00:24:53,240 --> 00:24:54,370
Every time I see you,

683
00:24:54,750 --> 00:24:55,680
you surprise me.

684
00:24:56,400 --> 00:24:57,550
Now I know

685
00:24:58,110 --> 00:25:00,040
what the difference is between us.

686
00:25:00,060 --> 00:25:01,130
It's courage

687
00:25:01,510 --> 00:25:02,640
and determination.

688
00:25:04,070 --> 00:25:05,200
It's more than that.

689
00:25:05,720 --> 00:25:07,310
There's also a gap of over 40 years

690
00:25:07,310 --> 00:25:09,370
and over 10 years of life experience.

691
00:25:10,510 --> 00:25:11,510
Comrade Xiaolan.

692
00:25:12,110 --> 00:25:13,070
Actually,

693
00:25:14,590 --> 00:25:15,400
it's been 3 months

694
00:25:15,400 --> 00:25:17,000
since I graduated high school.

695
00:25:17,000 --> 00:25:18,400
My family arranged

696
00:25:18,550 --> 00:25:19,880
a pretty good job for me.

697
00:25:20,350 --> 00:25:22,240
I should have reported for duty long ago,

698
00:25:22,240 --> 00:25:23,500
but I haven't gone yet.

699
00:25:25,310 --> 00:25:26,240
I can't quite say

700
00:25:27,030 --> 00:25:28,640
what exactly I'm hesitating about.

701
00:25:28,640 --> 00:25:29,550
You are hesitating

702
00:25:29,550 --> 00:25:31,110
because both
taking the college entrance exam

703
00:25:31,110 --> 00:25:32,040
and going to work

704
00:25:32,400 --> 00:25:33,960
are good options for you.

705
00:25:34,310 --> 00:25:36,030
In fact, taking the exam might look like

706
00:25:36,030 --> 00:25:37,110
taking a detour.

707
00:25:37,830 --> 00:25:39,240
You were going to work anyway.

708
00:25:39,240 --> 00:25:40,960
You'd have a good job without the exam,

709
00:25:40,960 --> 00:25:42,270
so why take the detour?

710
00:25:42,590 --> 00:25:44,110
But I'm different from you.

711
00:25:44,110 --> 00:25:45,440
If I don't take the exam,

712
00:25:45,440 --> 00:25:47,500
I can see the end of my life at a glance.

713
00:25:47,640 --> 00:25:48,500
I don't believe

714
00:25:48,590 --> 00:25:50,450
that I'm stuck like this forever.

715
00:25:50,510 --> 00:25:51,200
So,

716
00:25:51,440 --> 00:25:52,310
no matter how hard the exam is,

717
00:25:52,310 --> 00:25:53,200
I will try.

718
00:25:53,750 --> 00:25:54,350
Of course,

719
00:25:54,720 --> 00:25:56,720
I don't think it's hard for me.

720
00:26:00,960 --> 00:26:01,350
I...

721
00:26:01,750 --> 00:26:03,240
I haven't thought about it

722
00:26:03,510 --> 00:26:04,440
from this angle.

723
00:26:05,000 --> 00:26:06,000
Comrade Xiaolan,

724
00:26:06,400 --> 00:26:07,600
your words woke me up.

725
00:26:08,350 --> 00:26:09,080
In that case,

726
00:26:09,310 --> 00:26:10,170
after I go back,

727
00:26:10,550 --> 00:26:12,280
I will also seriously consider

728
00:26:12,400 --> 00:26:13,550
taking the college entrance exam.

729
00:26:13,550 --> 00:26:14,110
Oh no,

730
00:26:14,640 --> 00:26:15,970
I talked too much again.

731
00:26:16,400 --> 00:26:18,110
Being middle-aged really makes one

732
00:26:18,110 --> 00:26:19,440
love to lecture others.

733
00:26:21,830 --> 00:26:23,110
Whether you take the exam or not

734
00:26:23,110 --> 00:26:24,350
has nothing to do with me.

735
00:26:24,350 --> 00:26:25,750
I was just talking casually.

736
00:26:25,750 --> 00:26:26,880
I didn't give you advice,

737
00:26:26,880 --> 00:26:28,000
nor did I make any promises.

738
00:26:28,000 --> 00:26:29,130
Don't pin this on me.

739
00:26:32,400 --> 00:26:33,160
I do like you,

740
00:26:33,640 --> 00:26:34,400
but I don't need to

741
00:26:34,400 --> 00:26:36,060
gamble with my future, right?

742
00:26:37,310 --> 00:26:38,770
Don't feel too pressured.

743
00:26:40,270 --> 00:26:41,070
I swear to you,

744
00:26:41,440 --> 00:26:42,920
before you finish the exam,

745
00:26:42,920 --> 00:26:44,000
I won't bring up

746
00:26:44,000 --> 00:26:44,800
dating again.

747
00:26:46,070 --> 00:26:46,670
Of course,

748
00:26:47,400 --> 00:26:48,270
if

749
00:26:49,240 --> 00:26:50,240
one day I can catch up with

750
00:26:50,240 --> 00:26:51,160
your pace,

751
00:26:52,350 --> 00:26:53,950
then I hope you can seriously

752
00:26:55,000 --> 00:26:55,880
consider me.

753
00:27:01,480 --> 00:27:02,080
It's done?

754
00:27:02,160 --> 00:27:03,020
I exchanged it.

755
00:27:03,200 --> 00:27:04,200
A sleeper ticket.

756
00:27:08,050 --> 00:27:10,110
Sleeper tickets are hard to get, right?

757
00:27:10,110 --> 00:27:11,590
I didn't really need one—

758
00:27:11,590 --> 00:27:12,590
Comrade Xiaolan,

759
00:27:13,070 --> 00:27:14,200
I know you are smart.

760
00:27:14,750 --> 00:27:16,410
But for a young female comrade

761
00:27:16,440 --> 00:27:17,440
traveling away from home,

762
00:27:17,440 --> 00:27:19,040
one can never be too careful.

763
00:27:19,070 --> 00:27:20,240
From Shangdu to Longcheng,

764
00:27:20,240 --> 00:27:21,900
the train takes over 30 hours.

765
00:27:22,480 --> 00:27:23,480
And this time,

766
00:27:23,790 --> 00:27:25,350
I have things to wrap up too.

767
00:27:26,310 --> 00:27:28,030
I probably can't keep you company.

768
00:27:28,030 --> 00:27:28,590
So do not refuse

769
00:27:28,590 --> 00:27:29,790
this sleeper ticket.

770
00:27:30,310 --> 00:27:31,310
When you're away from home,

771
00:27:31,310 --> 00:27:32,270
safety comes first.

772
00:27:32,270 --> 00:27:33,440
It's not just for me,

773
00:27:34,440 --> 00:27:35,840
but also for your family.

774
00:27:36,750 --> 00:27:38,680
Attention, passengers.

775
00:27:38,880 --> 00:27:40,110
The train to Longcheng,

776
00:27:40,110 --> 00:27:41,480
No. 765,

777
00:27:41,640 --> 00:27:43,000
is now boarding.

778
00:27:43,270 --> 00:27:45,510
Please take your luggage

779
00:27:46,000 --> 00:27:47,250
and line up for ticket check.

780
00:27:47,250 --> 00:27:48,450
Give it to me. Thanks.

781
00:27:58,110 --> 00:27:58,840
Xia Xiaolan!

782
00:28:04,350 --> 00:28:05,000
Stay safe.

783
00:28:06,590 --> 00:28:07,070
Okay.

784
00:28:08,880 --> 00:28:09,410
Goodbye.

785
00:28:19,270 --> 00:28:20,700
From waking up in this spacetime

786
00:28:20,700 --> 00:28:22,160
to taking this step today,

787
00:28:22,310 --> 00:28:23,640
it's been only a month.

788
00:28:24,270 --> 00:28:25,240
My decisiveness

789
00:28:25,350 --> 00:28:26,350
and swift actions

790
00:28:26,920 --> 00:28:28,590
surprised not only those around me,

791
00:28:28,590 --> 00:28:29,720
but even myself.

792
00:28:30,590 --> 00:28:32,240
If the me from the original spacetime

793
00:28:32,240 --> 00:28:33,310
had such

794
00:28:33,310 --> 00:28:34,110
drive,

795
00:28:34,350 --> 00:28:36,160
would everything be different?

796
00:28:36,680 --> 00:28:38,070
Dear passengers,

797
00:28:38,240 --> 00:28:39,640
you are on

798
00:28:39,640 --> 00:28:40,880
the train to Longcheng,

799
00:28:40,880 --> 00:28:42,350
No. 765.

800
00:28:42,510 --> 00:28:45,400
We will pass through Xuxian, Xinyang,

801
00:28:45,640 --> 00:28:48,400
Changzhou, Yuezhou, and Changzhou.

802
00:28:48,750 --> 00:28:50,640
The next stop is Yuezhou.

803
00:28:50,640 --> 00:28:52,310
Yuezhou in this spacetime...

804
00:28:52,400 --> 00:28:53,750
Comrade, here is your meal.

805
00:28:53,750 --> 00:28:54,810
All right. Thanks.

806
00:28:59,920 --> 00:29:00,550
Comrade,

807
00:29:00,680 --> 00:29:02,070
would you like to order a meal?

808
00:29:02,070 --> 00:29:03,400
I'd like a cup of coffee.

809
00:29:03,750 --> 00:29:04,680
What?

810
00:29:06,590 --> 00:29:07,790
What do you have?

811
00:29:08,680 --> 00:29:09,680
Pork with peppers, 20 cents.

812
00:29:09,680 --> 00:29:10,680
Shredded potatoes, 10 cents.

813
00:29:10,680 --> 00:29:12,010
Braised fish, 50 cents.

814
00:29:12,240 --> 00:29:13,510
Pork with peppers, please. Thanks.

815
00:29:13,510 --> 00:29:13,920
Okay.

816
00:29:24,200 --> 00:29:24,750
Sister,

817
00:29:25,350 --> 00:29:26,410
you look educated.

818
00:29:28,030 --> 00:29:29,490
Traveling alone by train?

819
00:29:30,590 --> 00:29:31,850
Where are you heading?

820
00:29:32,110 --> 00:29:32,910
To Longcheng.

821
00:29:33,790 --> 00:29:34,790
Looking for a job?

822
00:29:35,790 --> 00:29:37,320
What kind of job do you want?

823
00:29:39,200 --> 00:29:39,650
[English]

824
00:29:40,790 --> 00:29:42,650
I want to do live streaming sales.

825
00:29:43,920 --> 00:29:45,180
Do you think I can do it?

826
00:29:45,750 --> 00:29:46,440
Sure.

827
00:29:47,160 --> 00:29:48,750
Any job you want is fine.

828
00:29:48,990 --> 00:29:50,350
I have connections.

829
00:29:50,550 --> 00:29:51,480
Leave it to me.

830
00:29:53,000 --> 00:29:53,920
Did you bring your letter of introduction?

831
00:29:53,920 --> 00:29:54,650
Let me see it.

832
00:29:55,790 --> 00:29:56,720
Like hell I will.

833
00:29:57,070 --> 00:29:58,470
What would I do with that?

834
00:29:58,640 --> 00:29:59,350
If I give you the letter,

835
00:29:59,350 --> 00:30:00,350
I'd have to give myself to you too, right?

836
00:30:00,350 --> 00:30:01,160
Crazy.

837
00:30:01,550 --> 00:30:03,720
What are you saying? I don't understand.

838
00:30:03,720 --> 00:30:04,920
Stop pretending.

839
00:30:06,000 --> 00:30:07,030
You're a human trafficker, aren't you?

840
00:30:07,030 --> 00:30:08,560
That trick won't work on me.

841
00:30:08,720 --> 00:30:09,960
Don't talk nonsense.

842
00:30:10,200 --> 00:30:11,440
If you don't want help, fine.

843
00:30:11,440 --> 00:30:13,030
You're treating my kindness like dirt.

844
00:30:13,030 --> 00:30:15,160
Trying to switch cars
to trick another lady?

845
00:30:15,160 --> 00:30:16,510
Everyone, be careful.

846
00:30:16,790 --> 00:30:18,440
This person is a human trafficker.

847
00:30:18,440 --> 00:30:19,000
Don't be—

848
00:30:19,000 --> 00:30:19,790
You're talking nonsense!

849
00:30:19,790 --> 00:30:21,110
Who are you calling a human trafficker?

850
00:30:21,110 --> 00:30:22,680
How can you make false accusations
when you're a kid yourself?

851
00:30:22,680 --> 00:30:23,830
You're terrible!

852
00:30:24,400 --> 00:30:25,370
I've heard that

853
00:30:25,680 --> 00:30:26,920
there are traffickers on trains now

854
00:30:26,920 --> 00:30:27,680
who steal children

855
00:30:27,680 --> 00:30:28,880
and trick women.

856
00:30:29,350 --> 00:30:30,160
When they see

857
00:30:30,160 --> 00:30:31,310
young women,

858
00:30:31,510 --> 00:30:33,030
they'd say they can bring them down south
to make big money.

859
00:30:33,030 --> 00:30:33,590
But in the end—

860
00:30:33,590 --> 00:30:34,510
All right, shut up!

861
00:30:34,510 --> 00:30:34,960
It's none of your business.

862
00:30:34,960 --> 00:30:35,240
Bro.

863
00:30:35,240 --> 00:30:37,300
There aren't that many traffickers.

864
00:30:37,790 --> 00:30:38,440
Yeah.

865
00:30:38,440 --> 00:30:39,700
This girl looks young.

866
00:30:39,790 --> 00:30:40,680
It's probably a misunderstanding.

867
00:30:40,680 --> 00:30:41,310
Let's just eat.

868
00:30:41,310 --> 00:30:42,160
A misunderstanding?

869
00:30:42,160 --> 00:30:44,400
You two are in on it together, aren't you?

870
00:30:44,400 --> 00:30:46,070
I think you're the one with the problem.

871
00:30:46,070 --> 00:30:47,160
Do you even have ID?

872
00:30:47,160 --> 00:30:47,790
Come on, let me see.

873
00:30:47,790 --> 00:30:48,750
Go away. Don't bother me.

874
00:30:48,750 --> 00:30:49,400
Where's your letter of introduction?

875
00:30:49,400 --> 00:30:49,920
Let go of me.

876
00:30:49,920 --> 00:30:50,920
Introduction...

877
00:30:51,030 --> 00:30:52,030
You're stealing my bag!

878
00:30:52,030 --> 00:30:53,000
What's going on? What's going on?

879
00:30:53,000 --> 00:30:53,800
Stop arguing.

880
00:30:54,590 --> 00:30:55,720
Behave yourselves!

881
00:30:56,920 --> 00:30:57,850
What's going on?

882
00:30:59,310 --> 00:31:00,000
Officer.

883
00:31:00,790 --> 00:31:01,750
This young lady

884
00:31:01,750 --> 00:31:03,070
was reading here.

885
00:31:03,680 --> 00:31:04,480
And this woman

886
00:31:04,480 --> 00:31:05,590
came over to chat her up.

887
00:31:05,590 --> 00:31:06,390
The two of them

888
00:31:06,480 --> 00:31:07,610
got into a conflict.

889
00:31:07,870 --> 00:31:09,270
I think for safety reasons,

890
00:31:09,270 --> 00:31:10,400
could you please check

891
00:31:10,400 --> 00:31:11,070
their IDs?

892
00:31:12,510 --> 00:31:13,550
Take out your IDs,

893
00:31:13,880 --> 00:31:14,410
tickets,

894
00:31:14,480 --> 00:31:16,200
and letters of introduction.

895
00:31:29,590 --> 00:31:30,320
Xia Xiaolan.

896
00:31:31,000 --> 00:31:31,440
Yes.

897
00:31:31,750 --> 00:31:32,720
Going to Longcheng.

898
00:31:32,720 --> 00:31:33,160
Right.

899
00:31:35,160 --> 00:31:35,640
Yours.

900
00:31:45,270 --> 00:31:46,470
Where's your letter?

901
00:31:46,510 --> 00:31:47,110
I-It's...

902
00:31:47,270 --> 00:31:49,350
in my luggage in the carriage.

903
00:31:49,750 --> 00:31:50,550
Bring it here.

904
00:31:52,590 --> 00:31:53,830
Go. I'll go with you.

905
00:32:03,750 --> 00:32:04,510
S-Sir.

906
00:32:07,480 --> 00:32:08,740
Thank you for earlier.

907
00:32:09,030 --> 00:32:09,680
You're welcome.

908
00:32:09,680 --> 00:32:10,480
When you're away from home,

909
00:32:10,480 --> 00:32:12,140
you really should be careful.

910
00:32:14,160 --> 00:32:15,440
You're just a little girl,

911
00:32:15,440 --> 00:32:16,840
but you've got some guts.

912
00:32:27,040 --> 00:32:28,070
Your pork and pepper rice.

913
00:32:28,070 --> 00:32:28,550
Thanks.

914
00:32:37,790 --> 00:32:38,920
Just you wait.

915
00:32:39,880 --> 00:32:41,240
You two useless idiots.

916
00:32:42,440 --> 00:32:46,470
[Yuezhou Station]

917
00:32:52,310 --> 00:32:53,310
I've long thought

918
00:32:53,550 --> 00:32:54,830
that in my old hometown

919
00:32:54,830 --> 00:32:57,160
there might be clues
about my time travel.

920
00:32:57,640 --> 00:33:00,240
But when I finally
saved enough for the ticket,

921
00:33:00,480 --> 00:33:01,480
I got cold feet.

922
00:33:04,070 --> 00:33:05,270
This coincidence

923
00:33:05,270 --> 00:33:06,400
getting off here

924
00:33:07,240 --> 00:33:09,550
might be destiny.

925
00:33:09,550 --> 00:33:10,030
Right?

926
00:33:10,200 --> 00:33:10,790
Why don't we pick

927
00:33:10,790 --> 00:33:12,030
some nice floral fabric first.

928
00:33:12,030 --> 00:33:12,960
Yeah, I think so too.

929
00:33:12,960 --> 00:33:13,560
Excuse me.

930
00:33:13,880 --> 00:33:14,880
I'd like to ask

931
00:33:15,240 --> 00:33:16,200
if you know

932
00:33:16,270 --> 00:33:17,530
someone named Liu Mei?

933
00:33:17,550 --> 00:33:19,350
She is a salesperson
at the winery's sales workshop.

934
00:33:19,350 --> 00:33:20,210
A salesperson?

935
00:33:20,920 --> 00:33:21,520
Xiao Song,

936
00:33:21,920 --> 00:33:23,590
is there a Liu Mei in your workshop?

937
00:33:23,590 --> 00:33:24,920
There's no such person.

938
00:33:25,160 --> 00:33:25,890
There isn't?

939
00:33:25,960 --> 00:33:27,680
Could you please think again?

940
00:33:27,920 --> 00:33:28,790
Think about what?

941
00:33:28,790 --> 00:33:30,680
There are only 5 of us in sales.

942
00:33:30,790 --> 00:33:32,190
I'd know if there was one.

943
00:33:33,400 --> 00:33:34,070
Thanks.

944
00:33:34,830 --> 00:33:35,590
Wang.

945
00:33:56,740 --> 00:33:59,920
My mom wouldn't paste
the "Happiness" character upside down.

946
00:33:59,920 --> 00:34:00,410
Hello.

947
00:34:00,830 --> 00:34:01,960
Who are you looking for?

948
00:34:01,960 --> 00:34:02,480
Hi.

949
00:34:03,080 --> 00:34:05,000
Does Xia Weimin
from Brewing Workshop No.4

950
00:34:05,000 --> 00:34:05,830
live here?

951
00:34:06,200 --> 00:34:07,200
You've got the wrong building.

952
00:34:07,200 --> 00:34:09,460
There's no one surnamed Xia in this yard.

953
00:34:09,960 --> 00:34:10,510
Dajuan,

954
00:34:10,840 --> 00:34:12,150
call Chaoying back for dinner.

955
00:34:12,150 --> 00:34:12,630
Okay!

956
00:34:13,219 --> 00:34:13,820
Chaoying,

957
00:34:14,000 --> 00:34:15,190
come home for dinner!

958
00:34:15,190 --> 00:34:15,590
Okay!

959
00:34:15,590 --> 00:34:16,790
Your dad made dinner.

960
00:34:18,800 --> 00:34:19,670
Hello, Miss!

961
00:34:45,630 --> 00:34:46,280
Xiaolan!

962
00:34:47,440 --> 00:34:48,239
What's wrong?

963
00:34:49,320 --> 00:34:50,050
Are you hurt?

964
00:34:50,250 --> 00:34:50,800
Get up.

965
00:34:50,800 --> 00:34:51,190
What happened?

966
00:34:51,190 --> 00:34:52,320
Let me see if you're hurt.

967
00:34:52,320 --> 00:34:53,050
Does it hurt?

968
00:34:53,070 --> 00:34:53,590
Don't cry.

969
00:34:53,590 --> 00:34:54,850
Did you drop your ball?

970
00:34:55,480 --> 00:34:57,080
There, there. Let's go home.

971
00:34:57,990 --> 00:34:58,870
Xiaolan, look.

972
00:34:59,150 --> 00:34:59,670
Catch!

973
00:35:01,000 --> 00:35:02,460
Kick it to Mommy, Xiaolan.

974
00:35:19,960 --> 00:35:21,190
This spacetime

975
00:35:21,440 --> 00:35:23,110
is exactly as I remember it.

976
00:35:24,440 --> 00:35:25,440
The difference is

977
00:35:25,920 --> 00:35:27,250
my parents aren't here,

978
00:35:28,070 --> 00:35:30,070
so the future me won't exist either.

979
00:35:31,320 --> 00:35:32,430
But I clearly carry

980
00:35:32,430 --> 00:35:33,800
memories of the past,

981
00:35:34,190 --> 00:35:36,000
and I was truly here.

982
00:35:37,190 --> 00:35:38,920
How do I describe this feeling?

983
00:35:40,550 --> 00:35:42,280
Homeless, rootless,

984
00:35:42,920 --> 00:35:43,800
with no ties—

985
00:35:44,400 --> 00:35:45,860
a completely fresh start.

986
00:35:47,760 --> 00:35:48,920
It's like a game,

987
00:35:49,400 --> 00:35:51,030
and I'm an experienced player

988
00:35:51,030 --> 00:35:52,690
who just opened a new account.

989
00:35:57,070 --> 00:35:59,190
Since I don't exist in this spacetime,

990
00:35:59,190 --> 00:36:00,250
then, Xia Xiaolan,

991
00:36:01,440 --> 00:36:02,710
I'm going to change our destiny

992
00:36:02,710 --> 00:36:03,760
and defy the odds.

993
00:36:42,490 --> 00:36:46,700
[Longcheng Train Station]

994
00:36:49,320 --> 00:36:50,150
Need a ride?

995
00:36:51,070 --> 00:36:51,930
Do you need one?

996
00:37:03,230 --> 00:37:04,550
Miss, need a ride?

997
00:37:04,550 --> 00:37:05,510
My car is brand new.

998
00:37:05,510 --> 00:37:06,360
No, thanks.

999
00:37:07,230 --> 00:37:08,110
Hey, beautiful.

1000
00:37:08,110 --> 00:37:08,800
It's free.

1001
00:37:08,800 --> 00:37:10,110
I'll take you wherever you want.

1002
00:37:10,110 --> 00:37:10,770
No, thanks.

1003
00:37:11,440 --> 00:37:11,840
Beautiful.

1004
00:37:11,840 --> 00:37:13,070
It's dangerous to be alone.

1005
00:37:13,070 --> 00:37:13,550
Come on.

1006
00:37:13,550 --> 00:37:14,000
Let me give you a ride.

1007
00:37:14,000 --> 00:37:15,230
I said no. Move.

1008
00:37:15,880 --> 00:37:17,280
It's dangerous for you to be alone.

1009
00:37:17,280 --> 00:37:17,920
Move!

1010
00:37:19,880 --> 00:37:21,000
Little girl, you're pretty tough.

1011
00:37:21,000 --> 00:37:22,280
Pretty girl, you're very tough.

1012
00:37:22,280 --> 00:37:23,340
Where are you from?

1013
00:37:34,440 --> 00:37:35,090
Bai.

1014
00:37:35,320 --> 00:37:36,650
You injured my brother.

1015
00:37:36,670 --> 00:37:37,150
Pay up.

1016
00:37:37,280 --> 00:37:38,460
You have to pay.

1017
00:37:38,920 --> 00:37:40,190
I'll pay you with a coffin.

1018
00:37:40,190 --> 00:37:41,150
Do you want it?

1019
00:37:42,000 --> 00:37:43,800
You might as well be dead.

1020
00:37:44,230 --> 00:37:45,330
Screw off!

1021
00:37:50,590 --> 00:37:51,230
Pretty lady,

1022
00:37:51,230 --> 00:37:51,960
are you okay?

1023
00:37:52,230 --> 00:37:52,760
I'm fine.

1024
00:37:52,880 --> 00:37:53,410
Let's go.

1025
00:37:53,710 --> 00:37:54,110
Okay.

1026
00:38:14,960 --> 00:38:15,560
Mr. Huang,

1027
00:38:15,780 --> 00:38:16,360
two bottles.

1028
00:38:16,360 --> 00:38:17,360
-I'll pay.
-Okay.

1029
00:38:20,190 --> 00:38:21,440
Have a soda. Cool off.

1030
00:38:23,630 --> 00:38:24,760
Thanks for earlier.

1031
00:38:24,840 --> 00:38:25,800
What should I call you?

1032
00:38:25,800 --> 00:38:26,710
My surname is Bai.

1033
00:38:26,710 --> 00:38:27,800
My name is Bai Zhenzhu.

1034
00:38:27,800 --> 00:38:28,320
I run

1035
00:38:28,630 --> 00:38:30,160
the fruit stall over there.

1036
00:38:31,360 --> 00:38:32,750
You seem older than me.

1037
00:38:32,880 --> 00:38:33,760
How about I call you

1038
00:38:33,760 --> 00:38:34,360
Sis Bai?

1039
00:38:34,810 --> 00:38:35,520
Sure.

1040
00:38:35,550 --> 00:38:36,550
Call me whatever you want.

1041
00:38:36,550 --> 00:38:37,750
You have great moves.

1042
00:38:39,150 --> 00:38:41,230
My family
used to run a martial arts school.

1043
00:38:41,230 --> 00:38:42,880
No one learns martial arts now.

1044
00:38:42,880 --> 00:38:44,800
My fellow disciples
have all changed careers.

1045
00:38:44,800 --> 00:38:46,320
Those guys just now

1046
00:38:46,440 --> 00:38:47,880
have been here for months,

1047
00:38:47,880 --> 00:38:49,210
making a mess of things.

1048
00:38:49,230 --> 00:38:51,150
I can't handle every petty theft.

1049
00:38:51,670 --> 00:38:53,000
But seeing you about to be kidnapped

1050
00:38:53,000 --> 00:38:54,070
in public today,

1051
00:38:54,070 --> 00:38:54,960
I had to step in.

1052
00:38:55,150 --> 00:38:56,510
Even though
the Bai Martial Arts School is gone,

1053
00:38:56,510 --> 00:38:58,000
we can't lose our sense of honor.

1054
00:38:58,000 --> 00:38:59,190
From your accent,

1055
00:38:59,190 --> 00:39:00,250
you're not a local.

1056
00:39:00,320 --> 00:39:02,280
Why did you come to Longcheng alone?

1057
00:39:02,280 --> 00:39:02,760
No,

1058
00:39:02,760 --> 00:39:03,760
I came with a friend.

1059
00:39:03,760 --> 00:39:04,890
She'll be here soon.

1060
00:39:05,400 --> 00:39:06,320
I'll wait with you.

1061
00:39:06,320 --> 00:39:06,960
No need.

1062
00:39:07,190 --> 00:39:08,190
I won't keep you from your business.

1063
00:39:08,190 --> 00:39:09,120
Please go ahead.

1064
00:39:09,830 --> 00:39:11,120
Find me if you need anything.

1065
00:39:11,120 --> 00:39:12,190
My stall is right over there.

1066
00:39:12,190 --> 00:39:12,850
Okay, sure.

1067
00:39:13,150 --> 00:39:13,800
Thanks.

1068
00:39:31,360 --> 00:39:32,430
I've heard

1069
00:39:32,430 --> 00:39:34,070
the clothing market in the 80s

1070
00:39:34,070 --> 00:39:35,270
was like a wet market.

1071
00:39:35,800 --> 00:39:36,480
It's true.

1072
00:39:53,150 --> 00:39:54,150
Okay, thanks.

1073
00:39:54,840 --> 00:39:55,970
Come and take a look!

1074
00:39:56,710 --> 00:39:57,320
Come on!

1075
00:39:57,920 --> 00:39:59,720
Everything over there is 5 yuan!

1076
00:39:59,760 --> 00:40:00,960
Sir, how much is this?

1077
00:40:01,360 --> 00:40:02,890
This one? Wholesale for 13.

1078
00:40:03,000 --> 00:40:04,230
Retail for 16.

1079
00:40:04,510 --> 00:40:05,550
Others sell it for 8.

1080
00:40:05,550 --> 00:40:06,510
Yours is too expensive.

1081
00:40:06,510 --> 00:40:08,000
Look at this fabric.

1082
00:40:08,030 --> 00:40:09,230
How can my clothes

1083
00:40:09,230 --> 00:40:10,760
compare to that cheap junk?

1084
00:40:11,250 --> 00:40:12,440
Where are you selling them?

1085
00:40:12,440 --> 00:40:13,630
It's not cheap here.

1086
00:40:13,800 --> 00:40:15,710
Be careful not to lose money.

1087
00:40:16,110 --> 00:40:16,960
To Yunan.

1088
00:40:17,230 --> 00:40:18,230
Yunan?

1089
00:40:19,960 --> 00:40:21,400
For Yunan, pick from over there.

1090
00:40:21,400 --> 00:40:22,110
Those over there are cheaper.

1091
00:40:22,110 --> 00:40:22,550
No, no.

1092
00:40:22,630 --> 00:40:23,920
We people in Yunan also need to wear

1093
00:40:23,920 --> 00:40:25,650
the most fashionable clothes.

1094
00:40:25,670 --> 00:40:26,400
Fair enough.

1095
00:40:26,760 --> 00:40:28,290
But let me be clear upfront.

1096
00:40:28,360 --> 00:40:29,960
If you can't sell them,

1097
00:40:29,960 --> 00:40:31,320
I don't accept returns here.

1098
00:40:31,320 --> 00:40:32,430
The styles are all here.

1099
00:40:32,430 --> 00:40:33,630
Pick whatever you like.

1100
00:40:33,630 --> 00:40:34,110
Okay.

1101
00:40:35,360 --> 00:40:35,960
By the way,

1102
00:40:36,190 --> 00:40:37,630
since you're selling in Yunan,

1103
00:40:37,630 --> 00:40:38,840
you surely won't have time
to come here often.

1104
00:40:38,840 --> 00:40:39,760
When you can't make it,

1105
00:40:39,760 --> 00:40:40,920
call the number on there to contact me

1106
00:40:40,920 --> 00:40:41,590
to place an order.

1107
00:40:41,590 --> 00:40:42,280
Okay, thanks.

1108
00:40:42,280 --> 00:40:43,440
Okay, take your time.

1109
00:40:43,440 --> 00:40:44,640
Sir, how much is this?

1110
00:40:44,880 --> 00:40:45,810
Coming, coming!

1111
00:40:46,190 --> 00:40:47,440
Everything is 5 yuan!

1112
00:40:47,550 --> 00:40:49,070
Wholesale here is also 5 yuan.

1113
00:40:49,070 --> 00:40:50,440
Retail is also 5 yuan.

1114
00:40:51,670 --> 00:40:52,510
Just 5 yuan.

1115
00:40:52,630 --> 00:40:53,710
That's the rock-bottom price, okay?

1116
00:40:53,710 --> 00:40:54,840
Rock-bottom price.

1117
00:41:01,110 --> 00:41:02,710
She really is a fruit seller.

1118
00:41:03,190 --> 00:41:04,800
Seems I was too guarded.

1119
00:41:06,710 --> 00:41:08,510
I still need to return the favor.

1120
00:41:08,630 --> 00:41:10,320
Cheap and good!

1121
00:41:12,590 --> 00:41:13,320
Ma'am, what—

1122
00:41:14,190 --> 00:41:15,130
Pretty girl!

1123
00:41:15,230 --> 00:41:16,230
It's you!

1124
00:41:16,580 --> 00:41:18,220
Sis Bai, I'm Xia Xiaolan.

1125
00:41:18,250 --> 00:41:19,360
Just call me Xiaolan.

1126
00:41:19,360 --> 00:41:20,480
Xia Xiaolan.

1127
00:41:20,800 --> 00:41:21,730
Hello, Xiaolan.

1128
00:41:22,480 --> 00:41:24,070
Are you done with your business?

1129
00:41:24,070 --> 00:41:25,470
Where's your companion?

1130
00:41:26,190 --> 00:41:27,840
She got her goods

1131
00:41:27,840 --> 00:41:29,170
and took the train back.

1132
00:41:29,960 --> 00:41:31,400
Our Longcheng longans

1133
00:41:31,510 --> 00:41:32,400
are delicious.

1134
00:41:32,660 --> 00:41:33,510
Here, try some.

1135
00:41:33,510 --> 00:41:34,030
Thanks.

1136
00:41:38,010 --> 00:41:38,920
Longans from 1983

1137
00:41:38,920 --> 00:41:39,670
are so sweet?

1138
00:41:39,800 --> 00:41:40,670
If you like them,

1139
00:41:40,670 --> 00:41:42,000
I'll give you some more.

1140
00:41:42,800 --> 00:41:43,760
No need, really.

1141
00:41:43,760 --> 00:41:44,280
That's enough.

1142
00:41:44,280 --> 00:41:45,590
-It's okay.
-It's too troublesome.

1143
00:41:45,590 --> 00:41:46,410
It's no trouble.

1144
00:41:46,410 --> 00:41:47,550
I'm just idling anyway.

1145
00:41:47,550 --> 00:41:48,760
There's no business right now.

1146
00:41:48,760 --> 00:41:49,110
I...

1147
00:41:49,480 --> 00:41:51,010
Take these to eat on the way.

1148
00:41:51,590 --> 00:41:52,070
Okay.

1149
00:41:52,440 --> 00:41:54,640
I can't just eat here and take some to go.

1150
00:41:56,110 --> 00:41:57,160
This piece of clothing,

1151
00:41:57,160 --> 00:41:58,190
you should take it.

1152
00:41:58,190 --> 00:41:59,540
Thanks for saving me just now.

1153
00:41:59,540 --> 00:41:59,950
Here.

1154
00:42:00,030 --> 00:42:01,190
Put it away, quick.

1155
00:42:01,320 --> 00:42:02,150
No, no, no.

1156
00:42:02,170 --> 00:42:03,110
I can't, I can't.

1157
00:42:03,360 --> 00:42:04,320
Put it away.

1158
00:42:05,840 --> 00:42:06,920
I just saw injustice

1159
00:42:06,920 --> 00:42:07,940
and stepped in to help.

1160
00:42:07,940 --> 00:42:09,010
If I take your stuff,

1161
00:42:09,010 --> 00:42:10,340
what would that make me?

1162
00:42:10,720 --> 00:42:11,440
When you go back,

1163
00:42:11,440 --> 00:42:13,190
you still need these to make money.

1164
00:42:13,190 --> 00:42:14,590
It's not easy for anyone.

1165
00:42:15,320 --> 00:42:15,710
Okay.

1166
00:42:15,840 --> 00:42:16,640
Then thank you

1167
00:42:16,880 --> 00:42:17,590
for this.

1168
00:42:19,320 --> 00:42:19,920
Sis Bai,

1169
00:42:20,510 --> 00:42:21,840
have you ever thought of

1170
00:42:22,230 --> 00:42:24,360
setting up your stall somewhere else?

1171
00:42:26,040 --> 00:42:27,520
Business was okay

1172
00:42:27,550 --> 00:42:28,810
in my previous spot.

1173
00:42:29,200 --> 00:42:30,040
But later,

1174
00:42:30,070 --> 00:42:31,920
a junior of mine got married,

1175
00:42:32,030 --> 00:42:33,760
so I gave the stall to the couple

1176
00:42:34,000 --> 00:42:35,860
and found another one for myself.

1177
00:42:36,190 --> 00:42:38,190
This place really isn't working out.

1178
00:42:38,190 --> 00:42:39,070
Then,

1179
00:42:39,440 --> 00:42:40,960
have you thought about switching trades?

1180
00:42:40,960 --> 00:42:41,840
I have!

1181
00:42:42,400 --> 00:42:44,060
I went to the clothing market.

1182
00:42:44,320 --> 00:42:45,800
Those bell-bottoms,

1183
00:42:45,800 --> 00:42:46,590
skinny jeans...

1184
00:42:46,590 --> 00:42:48,110
They make my head spin.

1185
00:42:48,110 --> 00:42:49,070
I don't get them.

1186
00:42:49,480 --> 00:42:50,670
It's all just to look pretty in,

1187
00:42:50,670 --> 00:42:51,730
but hard to work in.

1188
00:42:52,720 --> 00:42:54,040
You're right, Sis Bai.

1189
00:42:54,070 --> 00:42:55,150
But in the future,

1190
00:42:55,170 --> 00:42:56,280
people will be increasingly

1191
00:42:56,280 --> 00:42:58,360
willing to pay for things just for show.

1192
00:42:58,360 --> 00:43:00,070
You can predict the future?
